title: Hour 2 - Kevin O'Connell
itunes:title: Hour 2 - Kevin O'Connell
description:
Vikings HC Kevin O'Connell joins Dan to discuss what elements of his championship run with the Rams he is bringing to his new home in Minnesota. The guys play Find The Value and identify the best value plays for title picks in the NFL.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
